omp-comment-checker

This package is a fork of https://github.com/code-yeongyu/pi-comment-checker
v0.1.0 (copyright (c) 2026 Yeongyu Kim, MIT-licensed) retargeted at the
oh-my-pi (https://github.com/can1357/oh-my-pi) extension API published
as @oh-my-pi/pi-coding-agent.

The fork preserves upstream checker behavior and adds a self-heal loop
that uses two oh-my-pi-only affordances:

  * pi.appendEntry(customType, data)   - persists each unfired warning
    to the session file
  * pi.sendMessage(content, options)   - re-injects unfired warnings
    as a custom message on the next session_compact event

When the host does not provide those affordances (plain pi), the
self-heal loop is a no-op and behavior matches upstream 0.1.0
exactly.

The extension targets the public pi-coding-agent and oh-my-pi
extension APIs only and does not reach into internal modules of
either package.

